data.name: ReadCashReceiptDetail
data.value: select top(1) CRV_IDENTIFIER, CST_IDENTIFIER, CRT_IDENTIFIER, CRD_ID, COURT_ORDER_NUMBER from CKT_CR_DETAIL where (CRD_ID = @crdId) and (CRV_IDENTIFIER = @crvIdentifier) and (CST_IDENTIFIER = @cstIdentifier) and (CRT_IDENTIFIER = @crtIdentifier)

data.name: ReadCollectionCsePersonCashReceiptCashReceiptDetail
data.value: select T1.COLL_ID, T1.APPLIED_TO_CD, T1.COLL_DT, T1.ADJ_IND, T1.CONCURRENT_IND, T1.DISB_ADJ_PROC_DATE, T1.CRT_TYPE, T1.CST_ID, T1.CRV_ID, T1.CRD_ID, T1.OBG_ID, T1.CSP_NUMBER, T1.CPA_TYPE, T1.OTR_ID, T1.OTR_TYPE, T1.PREV_COLL_ADJ_DT, T1.OTY_ID, T1.COLL_ADJ_DT, T1.CREATED_TMST, T1.OB_TRN_AMT, T1.PGM_APPLD_TO, T1.CT_ORD_APPLIED_TO, T1.UNADJUSTED_DT, T3.CRV_IDENTIFIER, T3.CST_IDENTIFIER, T3.CRT_IDENTIFIER, T3.CASH_RECEIPT_ID, T4.CLT_IDENTIFIER, T5.CR_SRCE_TYPE_ID, T5.CODE from CKT_CRSRC_TYPE T5 join CKT_CASH_RECEIPT T3 join CKT_CR_DETAIL T4 join CKT_COLLECTION T1 on (T1.CONCURRENT_IND = 'N') and ( ( (T1.CREATED_TMST between cast(@timestamp1 as datetime2) and cast(@timestamp2 as datetime2)) and ( ( (T1.ADJ_IND = 'Y') and (T1.COLL_ADJ_DT > @collAdjDt) ) or (T1.ADJ_IND = 'N') ) ) or ( (T1.CREATED_TMST < @timestamp1) and ( ( (T1.ADJ_IND = 'Y') and (T1.COLL_ADJ_DT between cast(@date as date) and cast(@collAdjDt as date)) ) or ( (T1.ADJ_IND = 'N') and (T1.UNADJUSTED_DT between cast(@date as date) and cast(@collAdjDt as date)) and (T1.PREV_COLL_ADJ_DT < @date) ) ) ) ) and ( ( T1.OTY_ID in (4, 5, 6, 7, 8, 9, 15) ) or ( T1.PGM_APPLD_TO in ('AF', 'FC', 'NF', 'NC') ) ) and (T4.CRD_ID = T1.CRD_ID) and (T4.CRV_IDENTIFIER = T1.CRV_ID) and (T4.CST_IDENTIFIER = T1.CST_ID) and (T4.CRT_IDENTIFIER = T1.CRT_TYPE) and (T4.CLT_IDENTIFIER is not null) and ( T4.CLT_IDENTIFIER in (1, 3, 4, 5, 6, 10, 15, 19, 23, 25, 26) ) on (T3.CRT_IDENTIFIER = T4.CRT_IDENTIFIER) and (T3.CST_IDENTIFIER = T4.CST_IDENTIFIER) and (T3.CRV_IDENTIFIER = T4.CRV_IDENTIFIER) and (T3.CRT_IDENTIFIER <> 2) and (T3.CRT_IDENTIFIER <> 7) and (T3.CRT_IDENTIFIER <> 8) and (T3.CRT_IDENTIFIER <> 11) and (T3.CRT_IDENTIFIER <> 13) and (T3.CRT_IDENTIFIER <> 14) on T5.CR_SRCE_TYPE_ID = T3.CST_IDENTIFIER order by T1.CSP_NUMBER, T1.COLL_ID

data.name: ReadCsePerson
data.value: select top(1) T1.NUMB from CKT_CSE_PERSON T1 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_OB_TRN T3 with(readuncommitted) on (T1.NUMB = T3.CSP_SUP_NUMBER) and (T3.CPA_SUP_TYPE is not null) and (T3.OTY_TYPE = @otyType) and (T3.OB_TRN_TYP = @obTrnTyp) and (T3.OB_TRN_ID = @obTrnId) and (T3.CPA_TYPE = @cpaType) and (T3.CSP_NUMBER = @cspNumber) and (T3.OBG_GENERATED_ID = @obgGeneratedId)

data.name: ReadDisbursement1
data.value: select distinct top(1) T1.CPA_TYPE, T1.CSP_NUMBER, T1.DISB_TRAN_ID, T1.DBT_GENERATED_ID, T1.PRQ_GENERATED_ID from CKT_PMNT_REQUEST T4 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_DISB_TRAN T1 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_DISB_TRAN_RLN T2 with(readuncommitted) on (T1.DISB_TRAN_ID = T2.DTR_GENERATED_ID) and (T1.CPA_TYPE = T2.CPA_TYPE) and (T1.CSP_NUMBER = T2.CSP_NUMBER) and (@dtrPGeneratedId = T2.DTR_P_GENERATED_ID) and (@cpaPType = T2.CPA_P_TYPE) and (@cspPNumber = T2.CSP_P_NUMBER) and (T1.DBT_GENERATED_ID is not null) and (T1.DBT_GENERATED_ID <> 73) and (T1.DISB_TRAN_ID < @disbTranId) on (T4.PAYMENT_REQUEST_ID = T1.PRQ_GENERATED_ID) and (T4.TYPE = 'WAR')

data.name: ReadDisbursement2
data.value: select distinct top(1) T1.CPA_TYPE, T1.CSP_NUMBER, T1.DISB_TRAN_ID, T1.DBT_GENERATED_ID, T1.PRQ_GENERATED_ID from CKT_DISB_TRAN T1 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_DISB_TRAN_RLN T2 with(readuncommitted) on (T1.DISB_TRAN_ID = T2.DTR_GENERATED_ID) and (T1.CPA_TYPE = T2.CPA_TYPE) and (T1.CSP_NUMBER = T2.CSP_NUMBER) and (@dtrPGeneratedId = T2.DTR_P_GENERATED_ID) and (@cpaPType = T2.CPA_P_TYPE) and (@cspPNumber = T2.CSP_P_NUMBER) and (T1.DBT_GENERATED_ID is not null) and (T1.DBT_GENERATED_ID <> 73) and (T1.DISB_TRAN_ID < @disbTranId)

data.name: ReadDisbursement3
data.value: select distinct T1.CPA_TYPE, T1.CSP_NUMBER, T1.DISB_TRAN_ID, T1.AMOUNT, T1.DBT_GENERATED_ID from CKT_DISB_TRAN T1 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_DISB_TRAN_RLN T2 with(readuncommitted) on (T1.DISB_TRAN_ID = T2.DTR_GENERATED_ID) and (T1.CPA_TYPE = T2.CPA_TYPE) and (T1.CSP_NUMBER = T2.CSP_NUMBER) and (@dtrPGeneratedId = T2.DTR_P_GENERATED_ID) and (@cpaPType = T2.CPA_P_TYPE) and (@cspPNumber = T2.CSP_P_NUMBER) and (T1.DBT_GENERATED_ID = 73)

data.name: ReadDisbursementCollectionObligationTypeCsePerson

data.name: ReadDisbursementCsePersonCollectionObligationType1
data.value: select distinct T1.CPA_TYPE, T1.CSP_NUMBER, T1.DISB_TRAN_ID, T1.AMOUNT, T1.PROCESS_DATE, T1.CASH_NON_CASH_IND, T1.DBT_GENERATED_ID, T1.PRQ_GENERATED_ID, T1.REFERENCE_NUMBER, T11.CSP_NUMBER, T3.COLL_ID, T3.APPLIED_TO_CD, T3.COLL_DT, T3.ADJ_IND, T3.CONCURRENT_IND, T3.DISB_ADJ_PROC_DATE, T3.CRT_TYPE, T3.CST_ID, T3.CRV_ID, T3.CRD_ID, T3.OBG_ID, T3.CPA_TYPE, T3.OTR_ID, T3.OTR_TYPE, T3.PREV_COLL_ADJ_DT, T3.OTY_ID, T3.COLL_ADJ_DT, T3.CREATED_TMST, T3.OB_TRN_AMT, T3.PGM_APPLD_TO, T3.CT_ORD_APPLIED_TO, T3.UNADJUSTED_DT, T11.CSP_SUP_NUMBER, T6.CPA_TYPE, T6.CSP_NUMBER, T6.DISB_TRAN_ID from CKT_OB_TRN T11 join CKT_COLLECTION T3 join CKT_DISB_TRAN T6 join CKT_DISB_TRAN T1 join CKT_PMNT_STAT_HIST T8 on (T1.CASH_NON_CASH_IND = 'C') and (T1.PRQ_GENERATED_ID = T8.PRQ_GENERATED_ID) and (T8.EFFECTIVE_DATE between cast(@date1 as date) and cast(@date2 as date)) and (T8.DISCONTINUE_DATE >= @date2) and (T8.PST_GENERATED_ID = 6) join CKT_DISB_TRAN_RLN T10 on (T1.DISB_TRAN_ID = T10.DTR_GENERATED_ID) and (T1.CPA_TYPE = T10.CPA_TYPE) and (T1.CSP_NUMBER = T10.CSP_NUMBER) on (T6.DISB_TRAN_ID = T10.DTR_P_GENERATED_ID) and (T6.CPA_TYPE = T10.CPA_P_TYPE) and (T6.CSP_NUMBER = T10.CSP_P_NUMBER) on (T3.COLL_ID = T6.COL_ID) and (T3.OTY_ID = T6.OTY_ID) and (T3.OBG_ID = T6.OBG_ID) and (T3.CSP_NUMBER = T6.CSP_NUMBER_DISB) and (T3.CPA_TYPE = T6.CPA_TYPE_DISB) and (T3.OTR_ID = T6.OTR_ID) and (T3.OTR_TYPE = T6.OTR_TYPE_DISB) and (T3.CRT_TYPE = T6.CRT_ID) and (T3.CST_ID = T6.CST_ID) and (T3.CRV_ID = T6.CRV_ID) and (T3.CRD_ID = T6.CRD_ID) and (T3.CONCURRENT_IND = 'N') on (T11.OTY_TYPE = T3.OTY_ID) and (T11.OB_TRN_TYP = T3.OTR_TYPE) and (T11.OB_TRN_ID = T3.OTR_ID) and (T11.CPA_TYPE = T3.CPA_TYPE) and (T11.CSP_NUMBER = T3.CSP_NUMBER) and (T11.OBG_GENERATED_ID = T3.OBG_ID) and (T11.CPA_SUP_TYPE is not null) and (T11.CSP_SUP_NUMBER is not null) order by T11.CSP_NUMBER, T3.COLL_ID

data.name: ReadDisbursementCsePersonCollectionObligationType2

data.name: ReadDisbursementCsePersonCollectionObligationType3

data.name: ReadPaymentRequest1
data.value: select top(1) T1.PAYMENT_REQUEST_ID, T1.PRQ_R_GENERATED_ID from CKT_PMNT_REQUEST T1 join CKT_DISB_TRAN T2 on T1.PAYMENT_REQUEST_ID = T2.PRQ_GENERATED_ID join CKT_DISB_TRAN_RLN T3 on (T2.DISB_TRAN_ID = T3.DTR_GENERATED_ID) and (T2.CPA_TYPE = T3.CPA_TYPE) and (T2.CSP_NUMBER = T3.CSP_NUMBER) and (@dtrPGeneratedId = T3.DTR_P_GENERATED_ID) and (@cpaPType = T3.CPA_P_TYPE) and (@cspPNumber = T3.CSP_P_NUMBER)

data.name: ReadPaymentRequest2
data.value: select top(1) PAYMENT_REQUEST_ID, PRQ_R_GENERATED_ID from CKT_PMNT_REQUEST where PAYMENT_REQUEST_ID = @paymentRequestId

data.name: ReadWarrant
data.value: select top(1) T1.PAYMENT_REQUEST_ID, T1.TYPE, T1.PRQ_R_GENERATED_ID from CKT_PMNT_REQUEST T1 join CKT_DISB_TRAN T2 on (T1.TYPE = 'WAR') and (T1.PAYMENT_REQUEST_ID = T2.PRQ_GENERATED_ID) join CKT_DISB_TRAN_RLN T3 on (T2.DISB_TRAN_ID = T3.DTR_GENERATED_ID) and (T2.CPA_TYPE = T3.CPA_TYPE) and (T2.CSP_NUMBER = T3.CSP_NUMBER) and (@dtrPGeneratedId = T3.DTR_P_GENERATED_ID) and (@cpaPType = T3.CPA_P_TYPE) and (@cspPNumber = T3.CSP_P_NUMBER)
